name: The King's Dreams: Mordechai
description:
From a distance this would look like a great battle but if you were up close you'd see it was a celebration.
They chanted, jumped and danced.
They threw spears into the distance and had pseudo fights to display strength to their potential suitors in the crowd watching. How proud and valiant they all were. 
This grand ceremony was of the bravest and mighty and the colours of dust that came from their bare heels as they danced was a sight to behold.
They vibrated and moved into the night as the elders watched on and they were to continue this was until they tired and could leap no more.
